WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.533 --> 00:00:03.333
Xiaofeng

2
00:00:03.966 --> 00:00:06.566
I won't tell you to forget the past

3
00:00:06.666 --> 00:00:07.833
But you have to remember

4
00:00:08.133 --> 00:00:10.200
Your life is not your own

5
00:00:10.200 --> 00:00:11.300
Although we are discharged

6
00:00:11.300 --> 00:00:13.033
But we can only live for our country

7
00:00:13.066 --> 00:00:14.066
Die for battle

8
00:00:14.066 --> 00:00:16.500
So I will never allow you to abuse yourself

9
00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:17.700
But Captain

10
00:00:18.766 --> 00:00:20.100
My wife is dead.

11
00:00:20.133 --> 00:00:21.633
My son is in a coma

12
00:00:21.666 --> 00:00:23.166
I have been wronged for so many years

13
00:00:23.166 --> 00:00:25.466
I can't take it now

14
00:00:25.466 --> 00:00:27.066
So I let you go out and relax

15
00:00:27.066 --> 00:00:28.233
Forget these pains

16
00:00:28.266 --> 00:00:29.466
Time heals everything

17
00:00:29.466 --> 00:00:30.400
Finally.

18
00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:32.500
Believe me, I can.

19
00:00:37.900 --> 00:00:39.100
Until you forget your sadness

20
00:00:39.866 --> 00:00:40.866
Go back to the army

21
00:00:40.866 --> 00:00:42.266
I have applied to the old leader.

22
00:00:42.266 --> 00:00:44.100
The old leader agrees that you look back and come back

23
00:00:44.100 --> 00:00:46.100
Really, captain, I can still go back to the army

24
00:00:46.100 --> 00:00:47.766
When did my Qinglong captain experiment?

25
00:00:47.766 --> 00:00:49.166
Captain, I'm not going anywhere

26
00:00:49.166 --> 00:00:50.166
I want to go back to the army now

27
00:00:50.166 --> 00:00:50.933
Have you thought about it?

28
00:00:50.933 --> 00:00:53.766
You never need to consider returning to the army. I will arrange for you.

29
00:00:54.866 --> 00:00:55.700
Captain Xie

30
00:01:01.666 --> 00:01:03.000
OK, you go first.

31
00:01:06.333 --> 00:01:08.800
Nurse, this patient was discharged early this morning

32
00:01:08.800 --> 00:01:09.600
discharge

